{"tid":1686760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國據報提出在阿拉斯加或夏威夷簽署中美首階段貿易協議","createTime":"2019-11-01T10:52:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T11:03:38.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bc8f64c8ca9d3b7c3cea4f6094cb1c05fb43a891","tid":1686760,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489481-20191101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489481-20191101.htm&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=1af4a9fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489481-20191101.htm&h=6db1ac61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489481-20191101.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，美中兩國正在物色一個新地點，讓他與中國國家主席習近平，簽署首階段貿易協議，很快會有公布。<br />\n<br />\n有報道引述美方消息表示，白宮可能向中方提議，將簽署協議的地點，改至美國阿拉斯加或夏威夷，相信中方較易接受有關選址。早前有消息指出，中方建議將簽署地點改在澳門。<br />\n<br />\n另外，彭博引述消息人士報道，有中方官員對是否能與美國達成全面長期貿易協議，存在懷疑，質疑特朗普個性衝動，即使中美在未來數星期設法簽訂臨時協議，特朗普亦可能會出爾反爾，有報道亦表示，有中方官員私下透露，中國不會在最棘手的問題上讓步。"},{"pid":"699d12d7e5e83eb23be1c2861dc60f8a8b463f07","tid":1686760,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:55:57.000Z","msg":"中國自己唔反口都偷笑啦"},{"pid":"57dfd87566276ea9ec2dae4c1ef944a813987bbb","tid":1686760,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"最後揀新加坡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9423370d85766e76f9bf4dee11da1ae178ccd66","tid":1686760,"uid":36134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57dfd87566276ea9ec2dae4c1ef944a813987bbb","tid":1686760,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"最後揀新加坡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T10:58:44.000Z","ms